title: Grateful Dead Live at Knickerbocker Arena on 1993-03-29
description:
Set 1

Let The Good Times Roll, Feel Like A Stranger, Loser, Little Red Rooster, Ramble On Rose, Black Throated Wind, Lazy River Road, Johnny B. Goode

Set 2

Here Comes Sunshine, Looks Like Rain, Box Of Rain, He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> The Last Time*-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Liberty

*they started Miracle and changed their minds.
